[[File:Colonel Radick chathead.png|left]]
'''Colonel Radick''' is located in [[Yanille]] near the west gate and has extremely high [[hitpoints]] for his [[combat level]]. He is probably the Colonel of the Yanille Army. Nevertheless, he doesn't play any role in any [[quest]] despite being a unique character. When talking to him, he asks if the player is a friend or a foe. Of course, if the ''friend'' option is chosen, he will let you go but if the ''foe'' one is chosen, he will attack the player. When asked why Yanille is so heavily defended, he explains that as the southernmost city of [[Kandarin]] it must be protected from the [[Ogre]]s of the [[Feldip Hills]].

